name: $Quantity
desc: A coded concept from a reference terminology and/or text.

name: $integer
desc: A set of values bounded by low and high.

name: $Range
desc: A ratio of two Quantity values - a numerator and a denominator.

name: $Ratio
desc: A series of measurements taken by a device.

name: $SampledData
desc: A time during the day, in the format hh:mm:ss.

name: $time
desc: A date, date-time or partial date (e.g. just year or year + month) as used in human communication.

name: $dateTime
desc: A time range defined by start and end date/time.
